    <p>{`The `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://dev.splunk.com/enterprise/docs/dataapps/httpeventcollector/"
      }}>{`Splunk HTTP Event Collector (HEC)`}</a>{` is a fast and efficient way to send data to Splunk Enterprise and Splunk Cloud. Notably, HEC enables you to send data over HTTP (or HTTPS) directly to Splunk Enterprise or Splunk Cloud from your application.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "what-is-influxdb-logs"
    }}>{`What is InfluxDB Logs?`}</h3>
    <p><a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://www.influxdata.com/products/influxdb-overview/"
      }}>{`InfluxDB`}</a>{` is an open-source time series database developed by InfluxData. It is written in Go and optimized for fast, high-availability storage and retrieval of time series data in fields such as operations monitoring, application metrics, Internet of Things sensor data, and real-time analytics.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "strategy"
    }}>{`Strategy`}</h2>
